title: JULY 4TH BONUS: Miki Sudo Talks Nathan's Hot Dog Eating Contest
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Competitive Eater Miki Sudo sit down with Ebro in the Morning to discuss how she began, some of the records she holds, what strategy she uses while competitively eating, and her family of competitive eaters! She'll be participating at Nathan's annual Hot Dog eating process Monday, July 4 at Coney Island. 

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
